@CodeOps.Api_HostAddress = https://localhost:5000
@ApiVersion = 1.0

### Liveness
GET {{CodeOps.Api_HostAddress}}/health/live
Accept: application/json

### Readiness
GET {{CodeOps.Api_HostAddress}}/health/ready
Accept: application/json

### Example endpoint via URL segment versioning
GET {{CodeOps.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v{{ApiVersion}}/examples
Accept: application/json

### Example endpoint via header versioning
GET {{CodeOps.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v{{ApiVersion}}/examples
Accept: application/json
x-api-version: {{ApiVersion}}

### Example endpoint via query string versioning
GET {{CodeOps.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v{{ApiVersion}}/examples?api-version={{ApiVersion}}
Accept: application/json

### Versioned OpenAPI document
GET {{CodeOps.Api_HostAddress}}/openapi/v1.json
Accept: application/json

### Swagger UI
GET {{CodeOps.Api_HostAddress}}/swagger
Accept: text/html
